## 3. Mission Control Dashboard

Every brand partner accesses a unified command centre:

| Panel | Function |
|-------|----------|
| Inventory & Digital Goods | Upload, manage, and track all products |
| Questlines & Challenges | Build multi-step brand campaigns |
| Season Pass Manager | Design and launch 30-day passes |
| Boosts & Drop Days | Schedule multipliers and weekly releases |
| Loyalty Programme | Configure XP tiers and exclusive rewards |
| Bundles & Collabs | Build product bundles and manage partnerships |
| Creator Collab Hub | Hire verified creators for custom content |
| Analytics & Payouts | Real-time sales, engagement, ROI, and revenue management |

All analytics are privacy-safe. No personal data. No behavioural profiling. No surveillance.

