## 5. Revenue Model

| Revenue Stream | Description |
|----------------|-------------|
| Marketplace Fee | 5% on all digital goods sold |
| Boost Purchases | Brands pay BRICKS for reward multipliers |
| Listing Fees | 10 BRICKS per item listed |
| Premium Promotion | Brands boost visibility (paid in BRICKS) |
| Brand Subscriptions | Monthly fee for premium storefront features |

All fees flow into the treasury, funding the reward pool, platform operations, and community grants.

